= ⬡ QUARTER IV GATHERING — The Second Conjunction

*Theme:* End-of-Year Two review; transition into the Adept tier; opening of Golden Chain Book III.

#hm-note[
  This is a full ceremonial gathering. Allow ample time. The transition to the
  Adept tier is not merely administrative — it is an acknowledgment of two years
  of genuine work. The opening of GCH Book III should be marked distinctly: read
  the Preface together as a group before distributing the text. The declaration of
  Year Three focuses, heard collectively, creates a web of intention that will
  support each student's individual work throughout the coming year.
]

*Students bring:*
- Their long-circulating preparation: current state and observed changes since
  Month 9.
- Their metal meditation journal from Month 11.
- The opened Year One letter: a brief sharing of what they found there and
  what surprised them.
- Their declaration of Year Three focus: what thread of the mineral Work they
  will pursue, and why.

*The teacher formally acknowledges the transition to Adept tier.*
*The third Book of the Golden Chain is opened.*

